            <h2>2. Legal Ways to Resist and Advocate</h2>
            <p>Empower yourself and your community by participating in public consultations, organizing workshops, and advocating for transparency in campaign financing and algorithmic audits.</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Community Outreach:</strong> Host workshops and educational events.</li>
                <li><strong>Petitions:</strong> Support and create petitions calling for transparency.</li>
                <li><strong>Meeting with Lawmakers:</strong> Schedule discussions to express public concerns.</li>
            </ul>
